title: KULTDASHIANS w/ Casey Wilson
description:
Deep Divers, feast your ears on the first ever Bitch Sesh/Deep Dive crossover ep! Queens Danielle Schneider and Jessica St. Clair are away and the mice they will play! Casey and June Diane Raphael "dive deep" into The Deep End (The Teal Swan doc on Hulu) and do anything but "bitch" during their "sesh" about The Kardashians. See how fun this is already?? ENJOY!

Special thanks to Caitlyn Moldenhauer for editing this week's episode! 

Check out more Bitch Sesh here 

https://listen.earwolf.com/bitchsesh

 

Visit the Pinterest Board pinterest.com/thedeepdive

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod
